title: Once In A Zeit Moon 2/19: Kim and Kanye, King David, Snowflake, Johnny Damon, Icy Park

description:
On this edition of Once In A Zeit Moon Jack and Anna discuss Kim and Kanye officially calling it quits, Fox News threatening that Biblical figures are next to be cancelled and the internet saying "yup, okay", more details have come out about Ted Cruz' Cancun vacation, Johnny Damon getting a DUI, and the new Beyonce Adidas line is dropping today.
